title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 88-3.3 - Vacancies
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 88-3.3 - Vacancies

State Regulations

The director shall have authority to maintain such a number of vacancies as in his judgment will make adequate provisions for immediate admission of possible emergency cases. Notes
